\v 4 Lam sohwo Aminotap…®ye kan…®ngkwohweho.  
\p Aminotap sohwo Nasoun…®ye kan…®ngkwohweho.  
\p Nasoun sohwo Sal…®moun…®ye kan…®ngkwohweho.   
